                    Rev. Anderson (who removed to the country since)
 8.;
                    Benjamin M. Crump, 8—B. H.
                    Gotthelf, 8.

For the past four months, I am running around to collect for

                you and only the following have paid me: E. Lieberman, $8.;
                    M. L. Sale, $10.;

                S. SELLIGer, $8.; Abraham
                    Dinkelspiel, $10—together therefore $36.
